    "We use the MDS implementation from Graspologic (Chung et al., 2019) throughout.",
    "We use the profile likelihood of the singular values of D to determine the dimensionality of the DKPS (Zhu and Ghodsi, 2006) and note that this may be larger than two.",
    "We show only the first two dimensions for visualization purposes.",
    "Modern language models are trained with trillions of tokens of text (Touvron et al., 2023).",
    "For proprietary models such as OpenAI's GPT series or Anthropic's Claude series, the exact sources of the training mixtures are unknown and -given the models' propensities to produce content that is strikingly similar to copyrighted content (Henderson et al., 2023) -its curation and use is ethically questionable (Lemley and Casey, 2020)."
